name: #25-Kitty Camelot
description: Warrior of Kitty Verse, confuser by site, groves by day and divider of none by night.  This pretty Kitty Camelot is the maker, of the land known as Kitty Verse.  The Kitty to all Kitty's Kitty Camelot flies through Kitty Verse creating available space, sites and eatables.  The first Kitty ever - Kitty Camelot.
